<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.217285>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3 A – D: Clarkus sheri (Mulvey, 1967) Jairajpuri, 1970. A: Anterior end. B: Female genital branch (anterior). C: Vulval region. D: Female posterior end. E – H: Mylonchulus amurus Khan & Jairajpuri, 1979. E – F: Anterior region. G: Vulval region and posterior genital branch. H: Female posterior region (scale bars A, C – G = 20 µm; B = 50 µm; H = 10 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/217285/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

